lead_paragraph: Chicago Mayor Rahm Emanuel, a former White House aide to Presidents Barack Obama and Bill Clinton, on Friday joined the Ready For Hillary group that is urging former U.S. Secretary of State Hillary Clinton to run for president in 2016.

headline.main: Chicago Mayor Emanuel Joins Group Urging Hillary Clinton Presidency
